<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-us">
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1B1B1B;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #FAFAFA;
    }
    .email-container {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      padding-bottom: 24px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #E6E6E6;
    }
    .brand {
      color: #0b3d66;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .tagline {
      color: #757575;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #0b3d66;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .cta-box {
      background-color: #F5F5F5;
      padding: 32px;
      margin: 32px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #E6AF2E;
      color: #1B1B1B;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .alt-link {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #757575;
      margin-top: 16px;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #F9F9F9;
      border-left: 4px solid #0b3d66;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .info-box h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #0b3d66;
    }
    .info-box p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E6E6E6;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #757575;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="brand">Red Tape LA</div>
      <div class="tagline">Documenting LA's Building Bureaucracy</div>
    </div>

    <h1>Verify your report</h1>

    <p>Thank you for sharing your experience with LA's building process. We received your report about your <%= @report.project_type.presence || "project" %>.</p>

    <p>Before we can add your story to our database, we need to verify you're not a bot. Click the button below to confirm your email:</p>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <%= link_to "Verify My Report", @verification_url, class: "button", style: "background-color: #E6AF2E; color: #1B1B1B; padding: 16px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; display: inline-block;" %>
      <div class="alt-link">
        Or copy this link: <%= @verification_url %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h2>What happens next</h2>
      <p><strong>Weekly review:</strong> Our team reviews all verified reports and identifies patterns</p>
      <p><strong>Pattern analysis:</strong> We track which barriers are most common and which departments cause the longest delays</p>
      <p><strong>Advocacy action:</strong> We use anonymized data in meetings with city officials and publish reports every two months</p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Privacy:</strong> Your contact information stays private. We only share anonymized, aggregated data when advocating for reform.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Questions? <a href="mailto:contact@redtape.la" style="color: #0b3d66;">Email us</a></p>
      <p>Red Tape LA â€“ Building the case for housing reform</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
